{"id": 243221250, "title": "CG Pharmacy Celebrates First Anniversary", "text": "CG Pharmacy Celebrates First Anniversary CG Pharmacy celebrated its first anniversary with achievements, including winning \u201cThe Best in Bermuda\u201d award in the pharmacy category. A spokesperson said, \u201cCG Pharmacy, a key innovator in the pharmaceutical industry in Bermuda, proudly celebrates its first anniversary. This past year, the pharmacy has made significant strides toward its mission of providing affordable prescription medications, particularly benefiting seniors, the uninsured, and the under-insured. \u201cThis milestone is accompanied by the prestigious \u201cThe Best in Bermuda\u201d award in the pharmacy category, a testament to the community\u2019s trust and support.\u201d \u201cOur commitment to alleviating the financial burden of healthcare for the people of Bermuda has been our guiding principle since day one,\u201d said Naz Farrow, CEO of Coralisle Group. \u201cWinning \u2018The Best in Bermuda\u2019 award in our first year reaffirms that we are on the right path. This recognition by our customers is not just rewarding; it reinforces that our efforts to bring about better health outcomes are having a real impact.\u201d The spokesperson said, \u201cUnder the leadership of Jeremy Estey, Chief Operating Officer of CG Pharmacy, the pharmacy has built a reputation for exceptional customer service.\u201d \u201cWe are deeply honoured by this award and grateful to our customers who voted for us. It reflects not just the hard work of our dedicated team, but also our unwavering commitment to the community we serve\u201d said Estey. \u201cWe were unaware that voting was underway, so this came as a pleasant surprise. We have an amazing team who are passionate about the pharmacy care they provide and we want to personally thank our customers and the community members who voted for us.\u201d The spokesperson said, \u201cCG pharmacy remains dedicated to its role as a community-centered pharmacy, open to everyone in Bermuda. In addition to its exceptional customer service, CG Pharmacy offers free local delivery, a private consultation room for discreet and personal discussions, free medical reviews to help customers understand their medications better, and a wide range of popular over-the-counter products. These services ensure that CG Pharmacy not only meets, but exceeds the health and wellness needs of its clientele. For more information about CG Pharmacy, visit cgpharmacy.bm.\u201d", "summary": "CG Pharmacy celebrated its first anniversary with achievements, including winning &#8220;The Best in Bermuda&#8221; award in the pharmacy category. A spokesperson said, &#8220;CG Pharmacy, a key innovator in the pharmaceutical industry in Bermuda, proudly celebrates its first anniversary. This past year, the pharmacy has made significant strides toward its mission of providing affordable prescription medications, [&#8230;]", "url": "https://bernews.com/2024/06/cg-pharmacy-wins-best-in-bermuda-in-first-year/", "image": "https://cloudfront.bernews.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/CG-Pharmacy-Bermuda-June-2024-TWFB.jpg", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-29 00:10:07", "author": "temp", "authors": ["temp"], "language": "en", "source_country": "bm", "sentiment": 0.725}